{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the [BELARUSIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the brigada where I belonged to the partisans was Zhukov Brigade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I was working first in the kitchen and helping the other women to peel potatoes and other preparations of food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after a short while, they used me for other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the otriad, the brigade, went to-- to do-- I don't know-- to do-- I don't know how to say that-- actions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When they went to do the actions, that they had to destroy some train, or destroy some food, or knowing that they are transferring the Germans, they-- I would be taken with them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave me a rope, and if one of the soldiers was wounded, and-- I had to crawl, put that rope as possible around the person, and crawl back and bring that rope, that they could retrieve that wounded person.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this went on like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then, when they needed, they also put me on a patrol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And before the-- if anybody would get close, you had to ask their-- a certain-- it was-- you had to ask a-- a certain name-- word, that it was connected, that if they did not know, you were permitted to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this how I spent my time in the partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was summer, and we knew that the Germans began to retreat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was like in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew that soon, possibly, we are going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was in June when we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my brother and myself went to our city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we came there, of course, our homes were burned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But one of the houses of my cousin was still standing, and we went there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
